"ikony &kalarm-dopelniacz; na tacce systemowej."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:2349
#, no-c-format
msgid "Restore / Minimize"
msgstr "Przywróć/Minimalizuj"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:2350
#, no-c-format
msgid "Restores or minimizes the main &kalarm; window."
